<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>EMA616_02_IH_0002_s</title>

  <!-- 공통 js-->
  <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
  <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

  <!-- 공통 css-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

  <!-- 개별 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
  <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema511_01.css" /> -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema616_02.css" />
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema616_02_ih_0002">
    <section class="title type2">
      <h2 data-head="2_orange" lang="y">
        크기가 같은 쌓기나무를 쌓아 만든 두 직육면체의 부피를 비교하려고 합니다.
        <span class="circle_blank"></span>
        안에
        <img src="./../../common_contents//common/img/icon_arrow_right.svg" alt="크다" /><span class="ml-10">,</span> <img
          src="./../../common_contents//common/img/icon_equal.svg" alt="같다" /><span class="ml-10">,</span>
        <img src="./../../common_contents//common/img/icon_arrow_left.svg" alt="작다" />

        중 알맞은 것을 고르세요.
      </h2>
    </section>

    <section class="contents">
      <div class="flex justify_center">
        <div class="input_area flex dir_col">
          <div class="question_box img_box">
            <div class="inout_box">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_02_IH/616_02_02.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <span class="letter1">가</span>
            <span class="letter2">나</span>
          </div>
  
          <div class="question_box">
            <div class="inout_box">
              <div class="text">
                <span> 가의 부피</span>
                <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                  <select class="custom_dropdown math_symbol" data-answer-single=">">
                    <option></option>
                    <option value=">">></option>
                    <option value="=">=</option>
                    <option value="<">
                      << /option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <span> 나의 부피</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      

      <div class="solve_area">
        <div class="inner_solve">
          <div class="flex">
            <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
            <div class="conts_solve">
              <p>쌓기나무의 수를 세어 보면 직육면체 가는 24개, 직육면체 나는 18개입니다. 따라서 쌓기나무의 수가 더 많은 직육면체 가의 부피가 더 큽니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="btn_area">
        <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
        <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>

</html>